{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33030,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/01\/dua-for-ayat-sujud\/","url_meta":{"origin":35843,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sajdah: Supplication after reading a verse of prostration","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, prostrated after reading a verse of prostration in the Quran during the night prayer, he would say, \u201cI prostrate my face to the One who created it and brought forth its hearing and its seeing by His ability and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25486,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/30\/position-of-hands-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":35843,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Description of position of hands in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 30, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Wa\u2019il ibn Hujr reported: He saw the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, raise his hands upon entering into prayer, exalting Allah, and Hammam described his hands as parallel to his ears. Then, the Prophet wrapped his hands in his cloak and placed his right hand over his left\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19266,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/03\/sajdah-sujud-shaytan-weeps\/","url_meta":{"origin":35843,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sajdah: Satan weeps when believers prostrate","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen the son of Adam recites a verse of prostration and he prostrates, Satan withdraws and he weeps and he says: Woe to me! The son of Adam was commanded to prostrate and he prostrated, so\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37595,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/23\/sujud-above-ground\/","url_meta":{"origin":35843,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sajdah: The Prophet prostrates with body above ground","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 23, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Maymunah reported: If a calf wanted to pass beneath the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, when he prostrated, it could certainly pass through. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 496 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u0645\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0633\u064e\u062c\u064e\u062f\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0648\u0652 \u0634\u064e\